{"tid":924573,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"摩帥︰我們中場欠缺像狗的球員","createTime":"2018-12-02T08:10:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-02T10:46:42.000Z","uid":13797,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"bba4cb2564933eb1bfd2fcdbdc916c1416b6ef6b","tid":924573,"uid":13797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T08:10:09.000Z","msg":"周六英超尾場曼聯作客修咸頓雖開賽20分鐘便落後2球，但完半場前6分鐘內連追2球打和2︰2完場。賽後領隊摩連奴批評球隊中場欠缺壓逼，需要一些像「狗」的球員逼搶。<br />\n<br />\n賽後摩連奴認為球隊今場中場斷纜太多︰「我們中場多次失去控球，進攻最後3腳傳送做得不好，上半場最後15分鐘好了一點，但下半場又打回原型。」<br />\n<br />\n「他們不明白簡單足球是最好的，經常踢一些複雜足球，球隊的士氣和戰意是很好，像拉舒福特及菲爾鍾斯，但中場欠缺一些像『狗』的球員，去爭取皮球。」<br />\n<br />\n同時他亦讚賞交出2次助攻的拉舒福特︰「雖然他沒有入波但值得讚賞，把中場及進攻球員連繫，又努力防守，表現對得起這件球衣。」"},{"pid":"433c98f31c08c205a742f4e32818ff9d53ca4365","tid":924573,"uid":73422,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T08:11:05.000Z","msg":"獌狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a811e819f6cb03617916e4db1bb09e0ac8f1f12","tid":924573,"uid":111425,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T08:11:25.000Z","msg":"5 隻都未夠多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1e87680d6ae6416f7c5cd77e3c44027020ea9ed","tid":924573,"uid":18669,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T08:15:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39161c480ad667f10de73b769be3081f2945cd81","tid":924573,"uid":12000,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T08:16:49.000Z","msg":"佢自己落場踢咪有<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5106b5ed247c812bca862f83db4ecd3a9eb85cc1","tid":924573,"uid":214972,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T08:17:31.000Z","msg":"其實點解鬼佬都有癲狗依個concept<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2ba795f996842f0165bf9fe5e8f4bcfb5759932","tid":924573,"uid":95480,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedB